        <abstract> 
<p>Sends index [of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>, 2d ed.] with instructions for proof-reading.</p>  
<p>Asks GHD questions about heat transmission; he wants to use it as an analogy to illustrate transmission of motor impulses through leaves of <hi rend="italic">Dionaea</hi>.</p> 
